  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine yeast and 1 cup of warm water. Let sit for 5 minutes.",
    "Add bread, xenial cheese, beans, casseroles seasoning, salt, and pepper to the bowl. Mix well.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes or until the casserole is golden brown and the yeast is activated.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving."
